Phil Pennock wrote:
> What am I missing in the following example?
> 
> 		(${(j:|:)fred_list})

Change this to

                (${~${(j:|:)fred_list}})

to activate the `|'s.  The extra level of substitution seems to be
necessary to avoid the `|' in the (j:|:) having an effect too soon.

